front.title: •••Snowtrooper Officer
front.gametext: Deploy only on Hoth, but may move elsewhere. Snowtroopers are deploy -1 to same site. Your troopers may move to same Hoth site as a 'react.'
front.lore: Elite snowtrooper offers, like all Imperial Army officers, are well versed in Rebel tactics. They serve as infantry liaisons to AT-ATs.
